@startuml archive-plan-flow

title archive_plan mcp tool — 7 步原子收口 + baton cleanup 2 phase

actor Caller as C
participant "archive_plan handler\n(archive-plan.ts)" as H
participant "archivePlanImpl\n(archive-plan-impl.ts)" as I
participant "precheck-helpers" as PC
participant "index-sync-helpers" as IS
participant "sessionRepo (DB)" as DB
participant "runBatonCleanup\n(baton-cleanup.ts)" as BC
participant "sessionManager" as SM
participant "git" as Git
participant "fs" as Fs

== 入口:deny external + caller cwd 注入 ==

C -> H: invoke({plan_id, worktree_path, base_branch?, plan_file_path?, changelog_id?})
note right of H
  EXTERNAL_CALLER_ALLOWED.archive_plan = false
  stdio external client 直接 deny
  (写 git + 删 worktree 高风险)
end note

H -> DB: sessionRepo.get(callerSid)
note right of DB
  H5 修法: 反查 callerCwd + cwdReleaseMarker 注入到 implDeps
  fail-open: DB throw / row null → 退化 DEFAULT_DEPS + warnings.push
  (P5 R1 reviewer-codex HIGH-2 / REVIEW_56 §F9)
end note
DB --> H: { cwd, cwdReleaseMarker }
H -> H: mergeCallerCwd(callerImplDeps, sessionInjection)\n→ { deps, warnings: callerCwdWarnings }

== archivePlanImpl 入口 + 4 态预检 ==

H -> I: archivePlanImpl({planId, worktreePath, baseBranch, planFilePathOverride, changelogId}, mergedImplDeps)

I -> PC: precheck (4 态短路)
note right of PC
  4 态分流 (cwdReleaseMarker × cwd 在 worktree 内 笛卡尔):
  ① marker == worktreePath + cwd 在 worktree → pass (跨 adapter)
  ② marker == worktreePath + cwd 不在 worktree → pass (默认)
  ③ marker == null + cwd 不在 worktree → pass (无 marker)
  ④ marker == null + cwd 在 worktree → REJECT (cwd-resilience guard)
  + plan status != in_progress / worktree dirty / detached HEAD
  任一命中立即 return error (无部分回滚)
end note
PC --> I: precheck OK
I -> Fs: realpath + plan frontmatter parse\n(plan_id ↔ worktree_path cross-check, F2 fix HIGH)
note right of Fs
  F2 HIGH (REVIEW_59 批 A R2 反驳轮升):
  plan frontmatter.worktree_path != args.worktree_path
  → reject 防 silent corruption 双 plan 一起死
end note

== Step 1-5: 原子 7 步收口 (任一失败立即 abort 无部分回滚) ==

I -> Git: Step 1: git -C mainRepo checkout <base_branch>
note right of I
  base_branch 默认 = plan frontmatter.base_branch
  caller 未传时不再 fallback "main"
  (REVIEW_36 R2 user feedback 修法)
end note
I -> Git: Step 2: git merge --ff-only worktree-<plan_id>
Git --> I: ff-merge OK

I -> Fs: Step 3: write plan frontmatter\n(status=completed + final_commit + completed_at)
I -> Fs: Step 4: mv plan → <main-repo>/ref/plans/<plan_id>.md

alt spike-reports/ 存在 (Step 4.5)
  I -> Fs: detect <plan-artifact-dir>/spike-reports/
  I -> Fs: mv spike-reports/ → ref/plans/<plan_id>/spike-reports/
  note right of Fs
    F7 / F8 修法 (REVIEW_59 批 A):
    srcSpikeDir == dstSpikeDir guard (plan 已在 ref/plans/)
    EXDEV / perm 失败 → warnings.push hint (不阻塞 ok)
  end note
end

I -> IS: Step 5: sync INDEX.md (smart update 4 column)
note right of IS
  F6 修法 (REVIEW_59 批 A): RMW 单飞锁
  IIFE 包 async + .then(_,_) swallow + finally delete
  防 INDEX TOCTOU 并发写丢
  4 态: created / appended / updated / unchanged
end note
IS --> I: plansIndexAction

I -> Git: Step 6: git add + commit (pathspec 隔离: archivedPath + indexPath + planFilePath + spike-reports/)
note right of Git
  precheck mainRepo dirty 精确化:
  仅 reject 三 critical paths 命中 dirty
  其他无关 dirty 降 warning + commit message 注脚
  (F1b 修法)
end note

I -> Git: Step 7a: git worktree remove <worktree_path>
I -> Git: Step 7b: git branch -D worktree-<plan_id>

I -> DB: F10 修法: clearCwdReleaseMarker(callerSid) [提前到 Step 7 commit 后]
note right of DB
  F10 修法 (REVIEW_59 批 A):
  Step 7 (clearCwdReleaseMarker) 提前到 commit 后
  Step 8+ 失败时 marker 已清,caller 跑别 plan 不撞 stale marker reject
end note

I --> H: { archivedPath, commitHash, plansIndexAction, finalStatus, warnings, spikeReportsArchived }

== runBatonCleanup phase 1+2 (CHANGELOG_109 抽 helper) ==

H -> BC: runBatonCleanup({callerSessionId, toolName: 'archive_plan'}, {shutdownTeammates, archiveSession})
note right of BC
  phase 1 → phase 2 串行 await,helper 内部时序保证
  archive_plan 永远跑 phase 1 (plan 收口 = team 整片收口)
  (plan hand-off-session-adopt-teammates-20260520 P3 删 opt-out)
end note

BC -> SM: phase 1: shutdownTeammatesOnBaton(callerSid)
note right of SM
  caller 同 team 内所有 active + dormant teammate
  → sessionManager.close (dedup 跨 team 共享 sid)
  per-sid try/catch (单个 close failed 仅 warn 继续)
end note
SM --> BC: { closed: string[], failed: Array<{sid,reason}>, skipped: null | 'caller-not-lead' }

BC -> SM: phase 2: archiveCaller(callerSid)
note right of SM
  callerRow.archived_at 写 ISO ts
  failed: warn-only 不阻塞 ok return
  三态: 'ok' / 'failed' / 'skipped' (external)
end note
SM --> BC: archived: 'ok' | 'failed' | 'skipped'

BC --> H: { teammatesShutdown, archived }

== Handler 收口 ok return ==

H --> C: ok({\n  archivedPath, commitHash, branchDeleted, worktreeRemoved,\n  plansIndexAction, finalStatus,\n  warnings: [...callerCwdWarnings, ...result.warnings],\n  spikeReportsArchived,\n  archived,\n  teammatesShutdown\n})

@enduml
